OL,3,CM42 driver cheats death as huge metal
OL,4,Cmissile spears into camper van
OL,6,FA camper van driver was left screaming
OL,7,Fin agony after a massive lump of metal
OL,8,Fsmashed through his windscreen and
OL,9,Finto his body on the M42.
OL,11,FThe kingpin lock was thought to have
OL,12,Fcome loose from a lorry and speared
OL,13,Finto his van as the victim drove home
OL,14,Fwith his wife.
OL,16,FThe lock just missed Chris Benn's face
OL,17,Fafter he moved at the last second, but
OL,18,Fit broke his arm in six places and his
OL,19,Fwife Rachel claims he may never
OL,20,Fproperly regain its full use.
