OL,6,FThe 54-year-old could also be off work
OL,7,Ffor up to a year as he recovers, his
OL,8,Fwife Rachel said.
OL,10,FWarwickshire Police has urged
OL,11,Fwitnesses, or anyone with information,
OL,12,Fto come forward as the couple appealed
OL,13,Fto drivers with dashcam footage of the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,FHe suffered internal bleeding, needed
OL,17,Fblood transfusions and had surgery at
OL,18,Fthe Queen Elizabeth Hospital.
