OL,6,FThe couple were driving from Dorset
OL,7,Fwhen it happened on the M42 northbound
OL,8,Fbetween junctions nine and ten at
OL,9,Faround 2.30pm on Friday afternoon,
OL,10,FJune 21.
OL,12,FRachel said she heard an "almighty
OL,13,Fbang" and saw her husband's arm
OL,14,F"dangling" minutes after they had
OL,15,Fjoined the motorway near Water Orton.
OL,17,FShe said: "He saw it at the very last
OL,18,Fminute, and moved towards me to his
OL,19,Fleft, which then put his shoulder up
OL,20,Fand it hit that instead of his head.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
