OL,3,CM42 driver cheats death as huge metal
OL,4,Cmissile spears into camper van
OL,6,F"It went through his head rest. If it
OL,7,Fhad hit him in the face, that would
OL,8,Fhave been game over."
OL,10,FThe couple said that medics have
OL,11,Fpredicted Chris, a fridge and air
OL,12,Fconditioning engineer, will be off
OL,13,Fwork for as long as a year due to the
OL,14,Fseverity of his injuries.
OL,16,FTheir camper van has been left
OL,17,F"completely undriveable."
OL,19,FRachel, 46, said: "It was horrific.
OL,20,FWe'd just got on the M42, we'd only
OL,21,Fbeen on there for a matter of minutes.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
