OL,3,CM42 driver cheats death as huge metal
OL,4,Cmissile spears into camper van
OL,6,F"Our camper van was higher up, if it'd
OL,7,Fbeen a car it would have probably gone
OL,8,Fover the top.
OL,10,F"I was reading a Kindle so I didn't
OL,11,Fsee what happened, I heard an almighty
OL,12,Fbang and when I turned around there
OL,13,Fwas a hole in the windscreen and Chris
OL,14,Fsaid: 'My arm's gone'.
OL,16,F"He pulled the wheel and got us on the
OL,17,Fhard shoulder.
OL,19,F"Suddenly when the adrenaline wore
OL,20,Foff, he was screaming in agony.
