OL,6,F"We have been super-fortunate, it
OL,7,Fcould have been so much worse, but
OL,8,Fequally it shouldn't have happened."
OL,9,FEmergency services, including traffic
OL,10,Fpolice and an ambulance, were called.
OL,12,FAs they waited for the ambulance,
OL,13,FRachel went into the back to grab
OL,14,Fpainkillers, at which point she
OL,15,Fspotted the kingpin lock in the back
OL,16,Fof their van.
OL,18,FShe said: "It was heavy, I had to use
OL,19,Ftwo hands to pick it up.
