OL,6,F"It was covered in oil. It must have
OL,7,Fbeen coming towards us as it carried
OL,8,Fon coming through the back. When the
OL,9,Ftraffic police arrived, he said it was
OL,10,Fa kingpin."
OL,12,FChris was taken to Heartlands Hospital
OL,13,Fin "so much pain" before being
OL,14,Ftransferred to the Queen Elizabeth
OL,15,FHospital, where he remained on Monday,
OL,16,FJuly 1.
OL,18,FHe required blood transfusions due to
OL,19,Finternal bleeding and underwent an
OL,20,Foperation, Rachel said.
