OL,6,F"Chris had his operation, it all went
OL,7,Fas OK as it could do. There's just a
OL,8,Fbit of muscle the surgeon can't repair
OL,9,Fbecause there's a main artery
OL,10,Funderneath it.
OL,12,F"He might not ever get his arm back to
OL,13,Fgo over his head, and his job involves
OL,14,Fthat, so it's horrendous. They said
OL,15,Fnine to 12 months he'll be out of
OL,16,Fwork."
