OL,6,FRachel said: "If this (lorry driver)
OL,7,Fhas reached their destination, (they)
OL,8,Fmight be sat at home driving
OL,9,F(themselves) insane thinking (they've)
OL,10,Fkilled someone. It was awful, but it
OL,11,Fcould have been worse.
OL,13,F"It's going to affect our lives for a
OL,14,Flong, long time, but I don't want
OL,15,Fsomeone else's life affected as well,
OL,16,Fworrying (themselves) to death
OL,17,Fthinking (they've) killed someone.
